1
00:00:49,620 --> 00:00:53,820
=Camellias=

2
00:00:53,860 --> 00:00:56,780
=Episode 10=

3
00:01:02,479 --> 00:01:02,960
Feng Ye.

4
00:01:03,159 --> 00:01:03,799
Go save them!

5
00:01:06,799 --> 00:01:07,400
Feng Ye.

6
00:01:09,799 --> 00:01:11,680
You're targeting me like this

7
00:01:12,120 --> 00:01:12,840
only because you believe

8
00:01:12,840 --> 00:01:14,519
I wiped out your family.

9
00:01:15,280 --> 00:01:16,920
But have you ever considered

10
00:01:17,280 --> 00:01:18,959
that there's more to this?

11
00:01:22,519 --> 00:01:23,319
I saw it with my own eyes,

12
00:01:23,319 --> 00:01:24,560
and you talk to me about "more"?

13
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:37,200
Feng Ye.

14
00:01:44,959 --> 00:01:45,599
Move.

15
00:01:54,879 --> 00:01:56,400
General Rong,

16
00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:58,640
clad in armor,

17
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:02,640
seemingly impenetrable.

18
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:05,400
But beneath that iron shell

19
00:02:06,040 --> 00:02:09,039
lies a secret he keeps buried.

20
00:02:10,319 --> 00:02:12,439
Where there is a weakness in the heart,

21
00:02:13,199 --> 00:02:16,319
it will eventually show
in one's words and actions.

22
00:02:16,319 --> 00:02:17,520
You're like this,

23
00:02:18,080 --> 00:02:20,240
and so is Rong Zhaohua.

24
00:02:26,879 --> 00:02:27,639
My Lord learned

25
00:02:27,639 --> 00:02:29,039
that you, Minister Shen's family,

26
00:02:29,039 --> 00:02:30,039
were being unlawfully held

27
00:02:30,039 --> 00:02:30,919
by Rong Xiu, so he came to free you.

28
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:33,120
Thank you, My Lord!

29
00:02:34,759 --> 00:02:36,080
Thank you, My Lord!

30
00:02:36,080 --> 00:02:37,000
Thank you, My Lord!

31
00:02:44,919 --> 00:02:46,000
Jiang Yusang?

32
00:02:46,360 --> 00:02:46,919
No,

33
00:02:47,319 --> 00:02:48,319
you're her sister.

34
00:02:59,639 --> 00:03:01,159
Where is the Holy Maiden
and your General?

35
00:03:01,439 --> 00:03:02,439
Are you all deaf?

36
00:03:02,439 --> 00:03:03,639
My Lord is asking you!

37
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:06,039
Reporting, My Lord.

38
00:03:06,039 --> 00:03:07,159
The Holy Maiden took the General hostage

39
00:03:07,159 --> 00:03:08,120
and forced us to kneel

40
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:09,520
until they returned.

41
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:11,639
(She went after Rong Zhaohua.)

42
00:03:12,919 --> 00:03:13,840
Jiang Yukui,

43
00:03:14,199 --> 00:03:15,719
what are you trying to do?

44
00:03:16,879 --> 00:03:19,199
You shouldn't ask what I'm trying to do.

45
00:03:19,199 --> 00:03:20,319
Ask your brother

46
00:03:20,319 --> 00:03:22,159
what he is trying to do.

47
00:03:29,240 --> 00:03:29,879
Brother.

48
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:38,919
What's wrong?

49
00:03:44,560 --> 00:03:45,400
Zhao,

50
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:46,599
you're back.

51
00:03:47,319 --> 00:03:47,879
Brother.

52
00:03:48,199 --> 00:03:49,360
I'm Zhaohua!

53
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:51,840
I'm Zhaohua, brother.

54
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:52,319
Wake up!

55
00:03:52,319 --> 00:03:53,400
I'm Zhaohua!

56
00:03:55,080 --> 00:03:56,080
What's wrong with you, brother?

57
00:03:56,719 --> 00:03:57,400
Zhao,

58
00:03:58,680 --> 00:03:59,439
I'm sorry.

59
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:01,360
I shouldn't have killed you.

60
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:07,960
That blade piercing your body

61
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:10,520
hurts more than piercing my heart.

62
00:04:15,039 --> 00:04:15,960
Brother.

63
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:16,920
No!

64
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:18,240
Let me go.

65
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:18,720
Brother.

66
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:19,560
No!

67
00:04:19,720 --> 00:04:20,680
Brother!

68
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:22,680
I've already sent for His Majesty.

69
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:24,199
Guess

70
00:04:24,199 --> 00:04:25,920
when he sees this,

71
00:04:26,519 --> 00:04:28,240
how will he deal with you?

72
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:29,360
Your Majesty,

73
00:04:29,360 --> 00:04:31,040
a messenger from Consort Rong's palace

74
00:04:31,040 --> 00:04:32,120
reports that she's suddenly ill

75
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:33,120
and asks you to come.

76
00:04:34,279 --> 00:04:37,000
(The Emperor owes his throne
to the Rong family.)

77
00:04:37,720 --> 00:04:38,920
(When it comes to power,)

78
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:40,600
(trying to manipulate people's hearts)

79
00:04:41,240 --> 00:04:42,800
(is nothing but naivety.)

80
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:48,800
His Majesty arrives!

81
00:04:57,639 --> 00:04:58,399
There...

82
00:04:58,800 --> 00:05:01,199
There was an assassin
in the inner palace!

83
00:05:01,759 --> 00:05:03,839
Why is General Rong here?

84
00:05:04,120 --> 00:05:04,920
Your Majesty.

85
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:05,800
This...

86
00:05:10,519 --> 00:05:11,399
Guards!

87
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:13,680
Summon the imperial physician!

88
00:05:35,319 --> 00:05:35,920
How is she?

89
00:05:38,279 --> 00:05:39,120
Reporting, Your Majesty.

90
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:40,040
Consort Rong

91
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:41,360
was merely frightened.

92
00:05:41,439 --> 00:05:42,639
Her health is fine.

93
00:05:43,199 --> 00:05:43,879
However...

94
00:05:43,879 --> 00:05:44,399
Speak.

95
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:46,720
Congratulations, Your Majesty.

96
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:47,800
Consort Rong

97
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:49,480
is two months pregnant.

98
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:50,480
Pregnant?

99
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:51,519
I take my leave.

100
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:54,079
I'm going to have a child.

101
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:56,360
I'm going to have a child!

102
00:05:57,959 --> 00:05:58,879
Don't kill me.

103
00:05:59,279 --> 00:06:00,079
Don't kill me!

104
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:01,079
Brother.

105
00:06:01,399 --> 00:06:02,040
Brother.

106
00:06:02,199 --> 00:06:03,040
Don't kill me!

107
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:03,480
Zhaohua.

108
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:03,879
No!

109
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:04,759
Zhaohua.

110
00:06:04,959 --> 00:06:05,759
- Zhaohua.
- Brother.

111
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:09,360
Zhaohua.

112
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:09,680
Brother.

113
00:06:10,079 --> 00:06:10,519
Where is my brother?

114
00:06:10,519 --> 00:06:11,000
Zhaohua.

115
00:06:11,399 --> 00:06:12,040
Brother.

116
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:12,720
Where is my brother?

117
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:13,160
Zhaohua.

118
00:06:13,399 --> 00:06:14,120
- Zhaohua.
- Brother.

119
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:15,120
Calm down!

120
00:06:15,279 --> 00:06:16,319
General Rong is...

121
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:23,160
Zhaohua.

122
00:06:23,959 --> 00:06:25,160
You're with child now.

123
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:26,319
Rest assured.

124
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:27,560
This matter,

125
00:06:28,759 --> 00:06:30,279
I will see justice done for you.

126
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:40,680
Zhaohua.

127
00:06:41,160 --> 00:06:41,959
Rise.

128
00:06:43,079 --> 00:06:44,600
In all my years in the palace,

129
00:06:44,959 --> 00:06:46,279
I've never asked you for anything.

130
00:06:46,879 --> 00:06:48,879
Today, I ask only one thing.

131
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:51,000
Let me handle

132
00:06:51,959 --> 00:06:53,839
Jiang Yukui.

133
00:06:57,240 --> 00:06:57,759
Fine.

134
00:06:58,920 --> 00:07:00,000
I grant your wish.

135
00:07:00,839 --> 00:07:01,759
Now rise.

136
00:07:06,519 --> 00:07:08,360
I will give you justice.

137
00:07:09,040 --> 00:07:10,240
For now, focus on your pregnancy.

138
00:07:13,279 --> 00:07:13,839
Your Majesty,

139
00:07:13,839 --> 00:07:15,040
Lord Nine-Thousand requests an audience.

140
00:07:22,040 --> 00:07:23,120
Greetings, Your Majesty.

141
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,800
My dear minister, visiting
the palace so early.

142
00:07:25,160 --> 00:07:26,680
How unusual.

143
00:07:28,120 --> 00:07:28,639
I heard

144
00:07:28,639 --> 00:07:29,759
that General Rong Xiu

145
00:07:29,759 --> 00:07:31,519
was attacked last night
at Consort Rong's chamber.

146
00:07:32,920 --> 00:07:35,360
They say the assassin is
the Holy Maiden, Jiang Yukui.

147
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:36,879
You weren't in the palace,

148
00:07:36,879 --> 00:07:38,399
yet you know everything

149
00:07:38,399 --> 00:07:39,759
that happened here.

150
00:07:39,759 --> 00:07:42,040
The Holy Maiden has been
under my tutelage

151
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:43,680
and has been staying at my residence.

152
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:45,600
Last night, she did go missing.

153
00:07:45,600 --> 00:07:46,639
So I

154
00:07:46,639 --> 00:07:47,839
sent men to investigate.

155
00:07:51,879 --> 00:07:53,439
Look how nervous you are.

156
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:55,920
I was only making conversation.

157
00:07:56,120 --> 00:07:56,879
Jiang Yukui's assassination

158
00:07:56,879 --> 00:07:58,360
of Consort Rong and General Rong

159
00:07:58,360 --> 00:07:59,639
has been established.

160
00:07:59,639 --> 00:08:01,560
You needn't concern yourself further.

161
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:03,399
Your Majesty.

162
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:06,920
I find this matter highly suspicious.

163
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:08,360
Jiang Yukui is just a woman.

164
00:08:08,360 --> 00:08:10,120
General Rong Xiu is a seasoned warrior.

165
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:11,839
How could she have killed him?

166
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:15,399
You're awfully invested

167
00:08:15,399 --> 00:08:16,800
in this matter.

168
00:08:17,279 --> 00:08:19,040
That's unlike you.

169
00:08:19,480 --> 00:08:20,160
Everyone knows

170
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:21,600
that I and General Rong are at odds.

171
00:08:22,399 --> 00:08:23,040
And Jiang Yukui

172
00:08:23,040 --> 00:08:24,560
has been under my tutelage.

173
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:25,920
If something like this happens,

174
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:27,399
I can't escape responsibility.

175
00:08:27,600 --> 00:08:28,959
For my own innocence,

176
00:08:29,560 --> 00:08:31,480
I can't rest easy leaving this
to others.

177
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:35,360
Since you're so devoted,

178
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:37,600
I have a gift for you.

179
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:39,360
Guards.

180
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:21,879
You may have what you asked for,

181
00:09:21,879 --> 00:09:24,000
and I've kept my word.

182
00:09:24,559 --> 00:09:26,039
But as for anything else,

183
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:27,759
forget it.

184
00:10:01,159 --> 00:10:03,480
How do you like the Mirror Prison?

185
00:10:04,240 --> 00:10:05,519
Do you like it?

186
00:10:14,480 --> 00:10:16,879
You got lucky last time,

187
00:10:17,799 --> 00:10:19,720
but not this time.

188
00:10:20,679 --> 00:10:22,559
You and your sister,

189
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:25,200
neither of you can defeat me.

190
00:10:25,200 --> 00:10:27,000
You have no right to mention my sister!

191
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:28,840
You must be curious

192
00:10:29,080 --> 00:10:31,159
about how I treated her.

193
00:10:33,440 --> 00:10:34,480
Back then,

194
00:10:35,320 --> 00:10:37,200
right here in this Mirror Prison,

195
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:39,519
your sister

196
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:42,279
was violated by men I brought in

197
00:10:42,679 --> 00:10:43,600
until she died.

198
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:46,919
She looked at herself in the mirror,

199
00:10:47,720 --> 00:10:48,559
enraged,

200
00:10:48,799 --> 00:10:49,759
screaming,

201
00:10:50,279 --> 00:10:52,679
trying to use her so-called
Divine Power,

202
00:10:52,759 --> 00:10:54,600
but it couldn't save her.

203
00:11:01,320 --> 00:11:03,440
I used this very hairpin

204
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:06,080
to slash Jiang Yusang's face first,

205
00:11:06,519 --> 00:11:09,240
leaving countless scars on her body,

206
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:12,039
then presented her to His Majesty,

207
00:11:12,039 --> 00:11:13,279
and together, with him...

208
00:11:18,480 --> 00:11:20,720
First, it was your sister,

209
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:22,879
now it's you.

210
00:11:22,879 --> 00:11:25,480
You will both die by my hand.

211
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:27,159
To kill me,

212
00:11:28,399 --> 00:11:30,080
you didn't even hesitate
to sacrifice your own brother.

213
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:31,440
You killed him.

214
00:11:32,120 --> 00:11:33,279
What are you saying?

215
00:11:33,919 --> 00:11:35,559
The one who killed my brother

216
00:11:35,919 --> 00:11:37,200
was you.

217
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:39,240
His Majesty

218
00:11:39,240 --> 00:11:42,000
and all those guards saw it too.

219
00:11:45,120 --> 00:11:46,320
It was you.

220
00:11:47,039 --> 00:11:48,879
(I've already sent for His Majesty.)

221
00:11:49,440 --> 00:11:50,279
(Guess)

222
00:11:50,559 --> 00:11:52,159
(when he sees this,)

223
00:11:52,840 --> 00:11:54,320
(how will he deal with you?)

224
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:55,200
(No.)

225
00:11:55,200 --> 00:11:55,879
(Brother,)

226
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:56,840
(let me go!)

227
00:11:59,879 --> 00:12:02,120
(Why isn't my Divine Power working?)

228
00:12:06,759 --> 00:12:08,360
I was knocked unconscious.

229
00:12:09,480 --> 00:12:11,639
That night, it was only the three of us.

230
00:12:11,840 --> 00:12:13,279
Since it wasn't me,

231
00:12:13,639 --> 00:12:15,480
it had to be you.

232
00:12:17,600 --> 00:12:19,279
Everyone knows

233
00:12:20,120 --> 00:12:21,519
that Rong Xiu doted on me,

234
00:12:21,519 --> 00:12:23,279
his sister, above all else.

235
00:12:23,279 --> 00:12:25,440
He would die for me if he had to.

236
00:12:25,879 --> 00:12:28,399
So why would I kill him?

237
00:12:28,399 --> 00:12:29,960
General Rong,

238
00:12:29,960 --> 00:12:31,240
his love for you...

239
00:12:34,440 --> 00:12:36,840
I'm afraid it wasn't brotherly love.

240
00:12:55,460 --> 00:12:56,860
♪The moon sinks in the west♪

241
00:12:57,340 --> 00:12:58,780
♪The cold lamp burns low♪

242
00:12:58,980 --> 00:13:02,100
♪No one knocks upon
the mountain gate♪

243
00:13:02,420 --> 00:13:06,220
♪Snow-white winds and moonlight
touch me first♪

244
00:13:09,180 --> 00:13:10,900
♪Pear blossoms fill the courtyard♪

245
00:13:10,900 --> 00:13:12,420
♪Yet love and hate entwine♪

246
00:13:12,780 --> 00:13:16,180
♪Bound by precepts,
yet craving worldly desires♪

247
00:13:16,180 --> 00:13:20,180
♪Gathering red beans
for half a lifetime♪

248
00:13:21,340 --> 00:13:24,500
♪The Buddha speaks of countless paths♪

249
00:13:24,500 --> 00:13:28,060
♪How can one glance spanning ages
save a wandering soul♪

250
00:13:28,060 --> 00:13:30,380
♪Trapped within
the space between your brows♪

251
00:13:30,380 --> 00:13:34,580
♪Falling deeper and deeper♪

252
00:13:35,020 --> 00:13:36,660
♪The green lamp sheds no light♪

253
00:13:36,660 --> 00:13:38,180
♪Upon one who entered the path♪

254
00:13:38,180 --> 00:13:41,380
♪The six senses cannot cleanse
the dust of the past♪

255
00:13:41,780 --> 00:13:43,700
♪In dreams, it's you♪

256
00:13:43,700 --> 00:13:45,100
♪Beyond dreams, no one♪

257
00:13:45,100 --> 00:13:48,420
♪Clinging to one obsession,
adrift in a sea of suffering♪

258
00:13:48,420 --> 00:13:51,820
♪I can't forget
the stars in your eyes♪

259
00:13:51,820 --> 00:13:55,380
♪Our fate had already taken root♪

260
00:13:55,380 --> 00:13:58,620
♪In this mortal world, there is only us♪

261
00:13:58,620 --> 00:14:02,060
♪Hopelessly bound by love♪
